title: Are the Chargers Cursed?
itunes:title: Are the Chargers Cursed?
description:
A room filled with a couple of heroes- Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Colleen Wolfe & Gregg Rosenthal give you all of the latest news around the NFL including Chargers TE Hunter Henry suffering a torn ACL in practice (16:06), The New York Jets trading Christian Hackenberg to Oakland Raiders, (23:35) an amazing twitter fight, (33:35) and Richie Incognito being held on involuntary psychiatric hold. (40:19)
